        <li><strong>Placement:</strong> You must specify exact placement location. Changes after delivery may incur additional fees</li>
        <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> Delivery timelines are estimates. We are not responsible for delays due to weather, site conditions, customer unavailability, or carrier issues</li>
        <li><strong>Rescheduling:</strong> If you reschedule delivery more than once, additional fees may apply</li>
        <li><strong>Site preparation:</strong> You are responsible for site preparation (ground leveling, debris removal, access clearing). We can provide quotes for site prep services if needed</li>
